'''羅蘭·葛倫·「羅利」·芬格斯'''（{{lang-en|Roland Glen "Rollie" Fingers}}，{{bd|1946年|8月25日|}}），為美國職棒大聯盟的投手。生涯曾效力過運動家、教士和釀酒人等隊，芬格斯生涯共拿過3次世界大賽冠軍、7次入選明星賽、3次拿下大聯盟救援王以及4次拿下年度最佳救援投手獎。他還在1981年囊括賽揚獎和年度MVP等大獎。

芬格斯生涯共拿下341次救援成功，一度成為大聯盟紀錄，直到1992年才被打破。1992年，他順利入選名人堂，成為第二位入選名人堂的後援投手。而他的34號背號也被教士和釀酒人兩隊退休。
==職業生涯==
1968年，芬格斯登上大聯盟。<ref name="FlahertyT-TMJ-1990-12-20">Flaherty, Tom (December 20, 1990). – "What a relief for Fingers Manager's decision launched career that may land him in Hall of Fame". – ''[[The_Milwaukee_Journal|The Milwaukee Journal]]''.</ref>他在1970年站穩腳步，並先發19場比賽。<ref name="FingersR-B-R">[https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/f/fingero01.shtml Rollie Fingers] {{Wayback|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/f/fingero01.shtml |date=20210502194427 }}. – Baseball-Reference.com.</ref>1971年5月15日，他先是先發5局失1分。<ref>[https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/KCA/KCA197105150.shtml Athletics @ Royals – Saturday, May 15, 1971] {{Wayback|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/KCA/KCA197105150.shtml |date=20210308215453 }}. – Baseball-Reference.com.</ref>結果6天後，因為運動家先發投手Blue Moon Odom被打爆退場，使得芬格斯又上場後援5.1局。<ref>[https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/OAK/OAK197105210.shtml Twins @ Athletics – Friday, May 21, 1971] {{Wayback|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/OAK/OAK197105210.shtml |date=20210308131826 }}. – Baseball-Reference.com.</ref> 

同年5月底，總教練決定讓芬格斯擔任後援投手。<ref name="FlahertyT-TMJ-1990-12-20" />他在1973年僅先發2場比賽，其他比賽他大多在7局後登板。<ref>[https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/gl.cgi?n1=fingero01&t=p&year=1972 Rollie Ringers 1972 Pitching Gamelog] {{Wayback|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/gl.cgi?n1=fingero01&t=p&year=1972 |date=20160201082948 }}. – Baseball-Reference.com.</ref><ref>[https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/gl.cgi?n1=fingero01&t=p&year=1971 Rollie Ringers 1971 Pitching Gamelog] {{Wayback|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/gl.cgi?n1=fingero01&t=p&year=1971 |date=20160405052300 }}. – Baseball-Reference.com.</ref>

1972年到1974年，運動家達成現代棒球首見的三連霸。其中芬格斯獲選為1974年世界大賽的MVP，他在該系列賽拿下1勝和2次救援成功。

1974年世界大賽開打前，芬格斯曾因為妻子的關係和隊友Odom大打出手，結果造成芬格斯頭部縫了6針，Odom還扭傷了腳踝。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=M_ogAAAAIBAJ&pg=3717,2189434&dq=blue+moon+odom&hl=en|title=Fingers' Wife Triggers Fight with 'Blue Moon'|author=Milton Richman|date=October 12, 1974|publisher=The Hour|access-date=2021-04-01|archive-date=2022-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220206024001/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=M_ogAAAAIBAJ&pg=3717%2C2189434&dq=blue+moon+odom&hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>

1976年球季結束後，因為保留條款廢除，使得大聯盟出現許多自由球員，而芬格斯也是其中一位。當時球隊老闆原本打算將芬格斯和Joe Rudi交易到紅襪，[[維達·布魯|維達·布魯]]交易到洋基。結果大聯盟主席認為該交易案會破壞聯盟的平衡而駁回此案，使得球隊老闆怒告主席，並將3人強制坐冷板凳。後來因為3位球員用罷工來威脅，最後老闆才妥協讓他們上場。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://baseballhall.org/discover/going-deep/rollies-three-days-as-a-red-sox|title=Rollie Fingers' three days with the Red Sox|work=Baseball Hall of Fame|access-date=2017-06-20|language=en|archive-date=2017-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170804135242/http://baseballhall.org/discover/going-deep/rollies-three-days-as-a-red-sox|dead-url=no}}</ref>球季結束後，芬格斯以自由球員身分加盟教士隊。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2011/12/11/sports/baseball/veto-of-nba-trade-recalls-a-1970s-baseball-brouhaha.html?_r=0|title=When a Commissioner Becomes a Dealbreaker|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|first=Richard|last=Sandomirdec|date=December 10, 2011|access-date=July 26, 2015|archive-date=2015-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150403070917/http://www.nytimes.com/2011/12/11/sports/baseball/veto-of-nba-trade-recalls-a-1970s-baseball-brouhaha.html?_r=0|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=932&dat=19761126&id=N0RTAAAAIBAJ&pg=3078,4842313&hl=en|title=Kingman Daily Miner|via=Google News Archive Search|access-date=July 27, 2015|archive-date=2022-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220206024015/https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=932&dat=19761126&id=N0RTAAAAIBAJ&pg=3078%2C4842313&hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[File:Rollie_Fingers_-_San_Diego_Padres.jpg|alt=]]
1977年、1978年和1980年，芬格斯都拿下了國聯年度最佳救援投手獎。1980年12月8日，教士隊將芬格斯、Gene Tenace、Bob Shirley和一名日後指定球員交易到紅雀隊，換來Terry Kennedy、John Littlefield、Al Olmsted、Mike Phillips、Kim Seaman、Steve Swisher和John Urrea等人。<ref>{{cite web|title=Fingers, Tenace dealt to Cards|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=2199&dat=19801208&id=HKkyAAAAIBAJ&pg=4049,1713786&hl=en|work=Lawrence Journal-World|via=Google News Archive Search|access-date=July 27, 2015|archive-date=2022-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220206024044/https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=2199&dat=19801208&id=HKkyAAAAIBAJ&pg=4049%2C1713786&hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Trade Completed|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1893&dat=19801211&id=bHspAAAAIBAJ&pg=2673,5332188&hl=en|work=The Southeast Missourian|via=Google News Archive Search|access-date=July 27, 2015|archive-date=2022-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220206024026/https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1893&dat=19801211&id=bHspAAAAIBAJ&pg=2673%2C5332188&hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>結果才過沒幾天，紅雀便將芬格斯連同Ted Simmons和Pete Vuckovich兩人送往釀酒人，換來Sixto Lezcano、Lary Sorensen、David Green和Dave LaPoint等人。<ref>{{cite web|title=Brewers get Fingers, Simmons|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=757&dat=19801213&id=xA5OAAAAIBAJ&pg=5474,1783768&hl=en|work=The Virgin Islands Daily News|via=Google News Archive Search|access-date=July 27, 2015|archive-date=2022-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220206030821/https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=757&dat=19801213&id=xA5OAAAAIBAJ&pg=5474%2C1783768&hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>1981年，芬格斯囊括年度最佳救援投手、賽揚獎和年度MVP等大獎。1982年，雖然他拿下29次救援成功，不過也因為他大多抱傷登場，使得他無法參加釀酒人隊史首次的世界大賽，最後釀酒人輸給紅雀，無緣拿下首冠。1983年，芬格斯整年都在養傷，導致球季報銷。1984年8月，他還因為椎間盤突出動了手術。<ref>{{cite web|title=Rollie Fingers undergoes back surgery Friday|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1320&dat=19840801&id=55ARAAAAIBAJ&pg=5542,282995&hl=en|work=Gainesville Sun|via=Google News Archive Search|access-date=July 27, 2015|archive-date=2022-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220206030849/https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1320&dat=19840801&id=55ARAAAAIBAJ&pg=5542%2C282995&hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>

1985年9月17日，芬格斯完成最後一次登板。他被敲出1轟和送出1次三振。<ref>{{cite web|title=Milwaukee Brewers @ Baltimore Orioles – September 17, 1985|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/BAL/BAL198509170.shtml|website=Baseball-Reference.com|access-date=2021-04-01|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308135730/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/BAL/BAL198509170.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

球季結束後，芬格斯被釀酒人釋出。隨後他收到來自[[彼得·羅斯|彼得·羅斯]]的邀請，希望他能加入紅人隊。但是紅人隊女老闆Marge Schott卻以一句：「所有球員都要刮光鬍子才能上場。」這句話惹惱了芬格斯，並透過對方總經理直接向老闆開嗆：「妳如果把妳的聖伯納寵物犬的毛都剃光的話，我就刮掉我的鬍子。」<ref name="ArmoldE-YDR-2007-01-25">Armold, Elijah (January 25, 2007). – "A Man and His Famous Moustache: Hall of Fame reliever Rollie Fingers and his facial hair visited York Area Sports Night". – ''[[York_Daily_Record|York Daily Record]]''.</ref> Taking it even further, Finley came up with "Moustache Day" at the ballpark, where any fan with a moustache could get in free.<ref>Conklin, Mike (August 22, 2003). –  Chin music – The art and science of pitchers' facial hair." – ''[[Chicago_Tribune|Chicago Tribune]].''</ref>
==紀念==
[[File:Milret34.PNG|thumb]]
[[File:OaklandRetired34.PNG|thumb]]
1992年，芬格斯入選名人堂，成為史上第二位入選名人堂的後援投手。1999年，他被The Sporting News評為棒球百大傑出選手的第96名，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.baseball-almanac.com/legendary/lisn100.shtml|title=100 Greatest Baseball Players by The Sporting News : A Legendary List by Baseball Almanac|work=baseball-almanac.com|access-date=July 27, 2015|archive-date=2007-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070629064916/http://www.baseball-almanac.com/legendary/lisn100.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>並成功入選大聯盟世紀明星隊的最終決選名單。

而釀酒人和運動家都將芬格斯的背號退休，歷史上只有10位球員的背號能夠被兩支以上的球隊共同退休。

2000年，芬格斯入選聖地牙哥冠軍殿堂。
